  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in-- eventually in 1996 I published my first book on that, And I've just finished another-- another one is with an agent, and I'm working on a third, really a trilogy on this work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So intellectually, I was finding meaning for my life that involved both confronting the Holocaust but also seeing it as an intellectual challenge that wasn't being met.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also at that time, in the mid-1980s, I joined a Holocaust survivor group, a child survival group in the Baltimore-Washington area, where many of us battled the same battles of confronting the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm still a member.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the odd thing was in-- 10 years earlier, in the 1970s, I am convinced none of us would have joined a group like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the mid-'80s, we were all about ready to confront our personal stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Well, in a sense, the reason why I went to my village was to-- to end my beginnings, to forget the beginnings was really the reason why I went back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in one sense I was trying to forget the horrors, but also trying to clarify-- I was trying to forget them, to end them, and not necessarily to forget.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know whether I succeeded or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I would like to forget my fouled-up ways of handling life, my fouled-up ways of handling life, of-- particularly in Israel in relation to my family, I think I was not a good parent to my daughter during the '80s when sort of I was mentally wrapped up in my wrestlings, not that I would like to forget it, I would like to change it if I could, and I can't.",
      "word_count": 75
    }
  ],
